{"id":"41671e91d986e42cd417a76b051f4853d03c93de432ed2f5226dfc07f0684adc","item_id":"da03f10d01:0","text":"Projection Plugins（投影插件）是 RenderMan 观察数字场景所通过的 lens（镜头）。可以使用 C++ 创建 custom（自定义）projection plugins（投影插件）。RenderMan 自带多个 plugins（插件），其中 PxrCamera 是常用 projection（投影）。Omnidirectional Stereo projection（全向立体投影）会以适合 VR viewing（VR 观看）的格式渲染图像。"}
{"id":"6863067eb0a2c7499425c6c189b2c88bac55ca754285a6ab1ef37b75b4cfad4d","item_id":"da03f10d01:1","text":"参见"}
{"id":"1f8cd81ff995b025393180378c7ffe5e7a6922b81a8b1fea370c4b56538aef37","item_id":"da03f10d01:2","text":"Projection Plugins（投影插件）"}
{"id":"0895e3ea3d207f413c6e9c0870ef6824c14f2142a3f719d7dabf315b55a20792","item_id":"da03f10d01:3","text":"了解更多信息。"}
{"id":"44291877822d54ae9eed3e3bed076a28b8c97f74c7fa5b005fd923cccadf719a","item_id":"da03f10d01:4","text":"默认情况下，RenderMan for Blender 会使用下表映射默认的 Blender camera types（Blender 摄像机类型）："}
{"id":"f333db1a7e319b794d791112d0b7df2b8bd85c83f8ad46d84b05f966d45074ec","item_id":"da03f10d01:5","text":"Blender"}
{"id":"aa9f146c3d424a8c4b32f5ba83d79579f5d0892e81b6167e459582e2c1c8e4c4","item_id":"da03f10d01:6","text":"RenderMan"}
{"id":"e3ad1bcc2cbd85377f71f285a4b2d149459bd73272cbd4fe481123c02c494a08","item_id":"da03f10d01:7","text":"Perspective（透视）"}
{"id":"d8fdaddac09347f519f8255bcfa146273f7e61ad28f44c53264ae335d71bc2a3","item_id":"da03f10d01:8","text":"PxrCamera"}
{"id":"0f04d53421188d2467d0a42f725fa86f86a66b1f35b05308f94846be93fd59cd","item_id":"da03f10d01:9","text":"Orthographic（正交）"}
{"id":"ce1403ddc9601aeba624146b03ec7d25c650cce01028e75d3a0326c7018ef412","item_id":"da03f10d01:10","text":"PxrOrthographic"}
{"id":"7db3de914f23be178414fc9ef9573579b9dbc2131f04a2308496d77eba9c61e6","item_id":"da03f10d01:11","text":"Panoramic（全景）"}
{"id":"ab042143233de9f405239b4372ad20e7bdccdc37dec7876c7d8e9aa3c7332c8f","item_id":"da03f10d01:12","text":"PxrSphereCamera"}
{"id":"bf5a9a639ce8ef85a3f1471a4ddfa8f0fcb1db21690a2bf60ad413f3f4336835","item_id":"da03f10d01:13","text":"要显式设置 camera（摄像机）使用的 projection plugin（投影插件），请前往 camera data properties（摄像机数据属性），"}
{"id":"e7533fa13b1c41851f68a0a093c1da726b4355e4e0457e098e9ca9a9d75f26f0","item_id":"da03f10d01:14","text":"然后在 RenderMan Camera 面板下打开 RenderMan Projection 子面板，并点击 Add Projection Plugin。"}
{"id":"1c26befd01839132a403975007869c92e81e872a8c76e6e1c6a3152df14b3e4b","item_id":"da03f10d01:15","text":"接下来，选择你感兴趣的 projection plugin（投影插件），然后点击 OK。"}
{"id":"bc58c7603c6132169851116d3d4edca957450bb95be105fb3eda0fe30abcea71","item_id":"da03f10d01:16","text":"现在应能在面板中看到该 projection plugin（投影插件）的 parameters（参数）。"}
{"id":"f2b341af49e72a7d6ccad469f4ebd818a2ffa250a01bbb13436b5189331ff912","item_id":"da03f10d01:17","text":"注意，Use Camera FOV 选项会复制 camera（摄像机）当前使用的 field of view（视场角）设置，从而实际忽略 plugin（插件）上的 FOV 设置。这有助于匹配 viewport（视口）中该 camera（摄像机）的当前视图。"}
